{"article_id":"YcqxWwHJ1RPbsMQI","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Hurricane Florence","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"- the most powerful storm","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"to threaten the Carolinas in nearly three decades -","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"is expected to strengthen ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"say forecasters .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Officials warn","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"there is a chance of `` life-threatening inundation from rising water '' over the next 48 hours","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"as Florence heads for the US East Coast .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"With sustained winds of about 140mph","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"( 225km/h ) ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"the weather system is currently a category four storm .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"It could make landfall on Friday , near Wilmington , North Carolina .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Virginia , Maryland , Washington DC , and North and South Carolina have all declared states of emergency .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"`` This storm is a monster , ''","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"North Carolina Governor Roy Cooper told a news conference on Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"`` It 's big","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"and it 's vicious .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Hurricane Florence was 670 miles","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"( 1,078km )","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"south-east of Cape Fear , in North Carolina , as of 23:00 Atlantic Standard Time on Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"( 03:00 GMT Wednesday ) ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"according to the latest National Hurricane Center update .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The update says Florence","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"- which is moving north-west at about 17mph","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"( 28km/h ) -","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"is expected to strengthen on Tuesday night and on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"`` While some weakening is expected on Thursday ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Florence is forecast to be an extremely dangerous major hurricane through landfall , ''","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"it says .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Florence is expected to slow down considerably by late Thursday into Friday .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"The National Weather Service predicts potential storm surges of up to 13ft","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"( 4m )","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"on the coasts along with dangerously large swells and rip currents .","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"Hurricane-force winds will extend outward up to 60 miles from the centre and tropical-storm-force winds up to 175 miles .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"Rainfall could be up to 25in","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"( 64cm )","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"in some areas .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"This could worsen","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"if ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"as some meteorologists predict ,","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"Florence stalls","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"after it makes landfall .","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"The office of Virginia Governor Ralph Northam predicted `` catastrophic inland flooding , high winds and possible widespread power outages '' .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"The chief meteorologist for WCBD-TV in South Carolina , Rob Fowler , told the BBC","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that Florence was getting bigger ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"and those even 100 miles away would feel the impact .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Florence could rival the impact of Hurricane Hugo ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"which wreaked $ 7bn","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"( £5.3bn )","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"in damage","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"and claimed 49 lives in 1989 .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"It is also likely to affect the Brunswick Nuclear Plant in Southport , North Carolina ,","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"which is just a few miles from where Florence is expected to make landfall .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Mandatory evacuations have been ordered in parts of South Carolina , North Carolina and Virginia ,","depth":4},{"id":55,"text":"affecting more than a million people .","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"South Carolina 's Governor Henry McMaster initially ordered the entire coastline of his state to leave .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"However , the order was later confined to the northern coast .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"Residents of affected areas have been flocking to stores","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"to stock up on essentials .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"John Johnson , a hardware store manager in Charleston , South Carolina , told AFP news agency","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"there had been a `` nonstop '' rush on batteries , flashlights , plastic tarpaulins and sandbags .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Some petrol stations were running dry","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"as customers filled up .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Curtis Oil , a fuel distributor in Chesterfield , South Carolina , said","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"it had been `` overwhelmed with requests by state agencies and everybody else '' .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"US President Donald Trump has signed declarations of emergency for both North Carolina and South Carolina ,","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"freeing up federal money and resources for the storm response .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"Speaking in the Oval Office on Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Mr Trump said","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"the government would spare `` no expense ''","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"in responding to Hurricane Florence ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"the storm was `` tremendously big and tremendously wet '' .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Mr Trump also spoke of the US response to the aftermath of Hurricane Maria in Puerto Rico as `` one of the best jobs","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"that has ever been done '' ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"describing it as an `` incredible , unsung success '' .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"The description is in stark contrast to the assessment of Carmen Yulin Cruz , the mayor of the Puerto Rican capital , San Juan ,","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"who described Mr Trump 's response to the disaster as a `` stain on his presidency ''","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"after officials revised the death toll last month .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"The toll now stands at an estimated 2,975 people","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"- nearly 50 times the earlier figure of 64 .","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"That number includes those","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"who were killed directly by Hurricane Maria ,","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"as well as those","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"who died in the six months","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"following the storm","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"as a result of poor healthcare provision and a lack of electricity and clean water .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Repeated power cuts also led to an increased number of deaths from diabetes and sepsis .","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"The US government has a National Flood Insurance Programme","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"( NFIP )","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"that helps pay for flood coverage in high-risk zones across the country .","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"The programme ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"which is billions of dollars in debt ,","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"has been up for renewal several times -","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"Congress ' next deadline","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"to re-authorise the NFIP","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"is 30 November .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"While some wind damage may be covered by regular homeowners ' insurance ,","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"flooding is a different story .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"In the US , flood protection policies from private providers are often very expensive ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"largely because it is difficult to assess a home 's flood risk .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"These policies also take 30 days to kick in ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"meaning any homeowners","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"without coverage in the Carolinas","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"now will not be able to insure their property","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"before Florence hits .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"According to the Insurance Information Institute ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"14 % of Americans","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"living in the southern states","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"had flood insurance as of 2016 .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"No .","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"On the opposite side of the country , officials in Hawaii are warning residents and tourists to brace for the arrival of Tropical Storm Olivia .","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"Forecasters say","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"Olivia","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"- with current wind speeds of 65mph -","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"will make landfall on Wednesday morning .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"Schools and state parks have closed .","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"Ten to 15in","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"( 25 to 38 cm )","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"of rain is forecast for Big Island .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":241,"left":186,"right":240,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":186,"left":174,"right":185,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":137,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":132,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":128,"right":131,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":125,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":0,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"